<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>Get all/Search lookup lists</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"post"} path={"/v1/lookup-lists/search"}></MethodEndpoint>



Searches for lookup lists by name or ID. Can also be run without a filter to return the full list of existing lookups. Returns a paginated list of results. <br /> 
*Please ensure to change the region in the URL to match your account's region.*
